:03:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.twgreatdaily.com/imgs/image/176/17670214.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.twgreatdaily.com%2Fimgs%2Fimage%2F176%2F17670214.jpg&h=6dc993f8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"758bf0e5bdfcbdb7962ec9edd4e8ff17413a52a1","tid":1979673,"uid":228934,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T15:12:42.000Z","msg":"公務員比人清算，呢種中間級別就好易比人回血劍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n匹夫無罪，懷璧其罪。<br />\n<br />\n唔好以為政府就做唔出呢啲野，同共黨素有淵源既國民政府遷台初期就用呢招玩過啲公務員。<br />\n<br />\n當然共產黨點樣批鬥國民政府嘅公務<br />\n<br />\n杞人憂天？<br />\n<br />\n唔係因為你係公務員所以要清算你，而係你有小小錢，所以可以搵你開刀補貼收入。<br />\n<br />\n比個想搵筆快錢既京官睇中呢？佢做你冇成本架喎，屈你漏稅或者支持港獨，雙規什或刑求你一排，好似啲黑警抗斷手足幾條肋骨咁，唔會有仇報架喎。<br />\n<br />\n當然，香港局勢仲未糜爛到呢個地步，但係如果終有一日去到共黨可以直接管治香港既話，公務員絕對係比人搞既高危一族。"},{"pid":"34a3a7a577f667e011ddd74366bcb370cb5c3875","tid":1979673,"uid":60529,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T15:13:18.000Z","msg":"不了"},{"pid":"656c0162897544f8d867d54078ba0c5a06e018b8","tid":1979673,"uid":9193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T15:16:16.000Z","msg":"收皮啦"},{"pid":"67eec5a67da198381f2dc63a1ba3de3033ed7cc9","tid":1979673,"uid":51041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T15:17:18.000Z","msg":"好撚正呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92272e6722ea83efd6f1fa88eb36c6b2f5e335eb","tid":1979673,"uid":212897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T15:20:56.000Z","msg":"曱甴乸不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}